<p>To create a Spotlight component:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Choose "Add Spotlight Group" from the component drop-down.</li>
  <li>Fill in the "Spotlight" admin form. You can add up to 4 spotlights per group using the "Add Spotlight" button.</li>
  <li>Save the page.</li>
</ol>

